      "name": "Quote",
      "notes": "Standard entity in the Sales Pack module. Includes quote number, account, opportunity, status, valid-until date, addresses, line items (via separate QuoteItem entity), totals (subtotal, discount, tax, grand total). Status enum includes Draft / Presented / Accepted / Rejected / Expired.",
