      "is_standard": "true",
      "mechanism": null,
      "name": "Quote",
      "notes": "Standard object available in API version 18.0+. Each Quote belongs to one Opportunity. Quote Line Items mirror Opportunity Line Items. The \"Sync\" flag designates which Quote drives the Opportunity's Amount. Salesforce CPQ extends standard Quotes for complex subscription pricing, configurable products, and approval workflows.",
